#Generation17 Young Leader Nadine Khaouli (@NadineKhawli) is a co-founder of Lebanon-based @kafe_be_kafak, an organization that delivers food, medication and shelter to local communities. After last year’s blast in Beirut and the pandemic, Kafe be Kafak immediately went to work to help re-build local communities. Nadine believes we can use technology to be more connected and build a better future together.

To get involved, visit the #SamsungGlobalGoals app and visit us here:

Learn more about them and how to get involved here:  http://smsng.co/generation17_undp
